<h1 id=3D"galaxymakercheckerwidgetexpv1-3.Capability:Searchforapprovalworkf=
lows"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77=
);">3. Capability: Search for approval workflows</span></span></h1>
