 makers</li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "searchBy": "CreatedByAndCreatedOnDateRange",---&gt; Updated as part of=
 Feb 2026 ERM requirement
&nbsp; &nbsp; "workflowStatus": [
        "ApprovalPending",
        "Rejected"
    ],
    "types": [
        "w1cpayments"
    ],
    "subTypes": [
        "payments",
        "transfers"
    ],
    "createdOnDateRange": {           --------&gt; Introduced as part of Fe=
b 2026 ERM requirement
        "fromDate": "2019-08-24T14:15:22Z",
        "toDate": "2019-08-24T14:15:22Z"
    },
    "requestGroup": "Customer",
    "approvalChannel": "W1C-Customer"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p>2. <span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"31f096f3-33a1-4abb-=
956e-854109d4ad19">Request Payload</span> to search for workflow requests a=
waiting approval from checkers along side requests that are rejected.</p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "searchBy": "ApproverAndCreatedOnDateRange",--&gt; Updated as part of F=
eb 2026 ERM requirement
&nbsp; &nbsp; "approverStatus": [
        "ApprovalPending",
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;"Rejected"=20
&nbsp; &nbsp; ],
&nbsp; &nbsp; "workflowStatus": [
        "ApprovalPending",
        "Rejected"
    ],
&nbsp; &nbsp; "types": [
        "w1cpayments"
    ],
    "subTypes": [
        "payments"
    ],
    "createdOnDateRange": {           --------&gt; Introduced as part of FE=
B 2026 ERM requirement
        "fromDate": "2019-08-24T14:15:22Z",
        "toDate": "2019-08-24T14:15:22Z"
    },
    "requestGroup": "Customer",
    "approvalChannel": "W1C-Customer"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><u><strong>Nov 2025 ERM Changes</stro=
ng></u></span></p>
<p>As part of Nov 2025 ERM requirements, CreatedOnDateRange filter will be =
introduced in the UI which will allow users to search for workflow requests=
 within the specified date range. The SD for this requirement can be found =
here:&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href=3D"/display/ARTC/SD+%3A+Search+capabilities+for+customer+portal+=
lists#SD:Searchcapabilitiesforcustomerportallists-PaymentsAuthorisationList=
">SD : Search capabilities for customer portal lists#PaymentsAuthorisationL=
ist</a></p>
<p><a href=3D"/display/ARTC/SD+%3A+Search+capabilities+for+customer+portal+=
lists#SD:Searchcapabilitiesforcustomerportallists-BeneficiaryAuthorisationL=
ist">SD : Search capabilities for customer portal lists#BeneficiaryAuthoris=
ationList</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong><u><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);">Aug 2026 ERM Changes</sp=
an></u></strong></p>
<p>As part of Aug 2026 ERM requirements, cutOffTime field will be added to =
the response payload for RTGS payment.</p>
<p>( i.e. supplementaryData.paymentDomainMetadata.paymentProductId</p>
<p>=3D=3D "<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">PP000001" )</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">if system time is between 3:00 PM =
and 3:59 PM (AEST) return "16:00" otherwise return null/empty.</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><u><strong>Feb 2026 ERM:</strong></=
u></span> As part of search capabilities(SD:&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://conflu=
ence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/SD+%3A+Search+capabilities+for+custome=
r+portal+lists#SD:Searchcapabilitiesforcustomerportallists-PaymentsAuthoris=
ationList" rel=3D"nofollow">SD : Search capabilities for customer portal li=
sts - PaymentsAuthorisationList</a> &amp; <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv=
.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/SD+%3A+Search+capabilities+for+customer+portal=
+lists#SD:Searchcapabilitiesforcustomerportallists-BeneficiaryAuthorisation=
List" rel=3D"nofollow">SD : Search capabilities for customer portal lists -=
 BeneficiaryAuthorisationList</a>), to enable search alongside DateRange, t=
he searchBy will be updated to the following,</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>To get maker request with the supplied date range, the searchBy should =
be set to "<span style=3D"color: rgb(36,36,36);">CreatedByAndCreatedOnDateR=
ange</span>"</li>
<li>To get checker request with the supplied date range, the searchBy shoul=
d be set to "<span style=3D"color: rgb(36,36,36);">ApproverAndCreatedOnDate=
Range</span>"</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p>DSR supports the following enum for&nbsp;<strong>searchBy</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>ApprovalWorflowIds</li>
<li>CreatedBy</li>
<li>Approver</li>
<li>OnBehalfOf</li>
<li>ApproverAndCreatedOnDateRange</li>
<li>OnBehalfOfUserAndCreatedOnDateRange</li>
</ul>
<p>For maker, UI should should send <strong>searchBy =3D "createdBy"</stron=
g></p>
<p>For checker, UI should should send <strong>searchBy =3D "approver"</stro=
ng></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>DSR supports the following enum for <strong>workflowStatus</strong> &amp=
; <strong>approverStatus</strong> :</p>
<ul>
<li>ApprovalPending</li>
<li>Approved</li>
<li>Rejected</li>
<li>Expired</li>
<li>Cancelled</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Type</strong> and <strong>SubType </strong>ERDM values as accept=
ed by DSR are as below,</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable" data-mce-resize=3D"false">
<colgroup>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">w1cpayments</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">w1cbeneficiary</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable" data-mce-resize=3D"false">
<colgroup>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">SubType</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">payments</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">transfers</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">addbeneficiary</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">amendbeneficiary</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">archivebeneficiary</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p>The corresponding DSR request for make and checker will be as below.</p>
<p><br></p>
<ol>
<li>Maker request body to search for workflow requests in "ApprovalPending"=
 and "Rejected" status=20
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "searchBy": "createdBy",
    "createdByUserId": "4566789",
&nbsp; &nbsp; "workflowStatus": [
        "ApprovalPending",
        "Rejected"
    ],
    "types": [
        "w1cpayments"
    ],
    "subTypes": [
        "payments",
        "transfers"
    ],
    "createdOnDateRange": {           --------&gt; Introduced as part of FE=
B 2026 ERM requirement
        "fromDate": "2019-08-24T14:15:22Z",
        "toDate": "2019-08-24T14:15:22Z"
    },
    "requestGroup": "Customer",
    "approvalChannel" : "W1C-Customer"
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li>Checker request body to search for workflow requests that are awaiting =
checker approval along side requests that are rejected=20
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "searchBy": "approver",
 &nbsp;  "approverUserId": "4566789",
&nbsp; &nbsp; "approverStatus": [
        "ApprovalPending"
    ],
 &nbsp; &nbsp;"workflowStatus": [
        "ApprovalPending",
        "Rejected"
    ],
&nbsp; &nbsp; "types": [
        "W1C Payments"
    ],
    "subTypes": [
        "Payments"
    ],
     "createdOnDateRange": {           --------&gt; Introduced as part of F=
EB 2026 ERM requirement
        "fromDate": "2019-08-24T14:15:22Z",
        "toDate": "2019-08-24T14:15:22Z"
    },
    "requestGroup": "Customer",
    "approvalChannel": "W1C-Customer"
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ol>
<pre><br></pre>
<pre><br></pre>
<pre><br></pre>
</div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
