</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Even though this header is not mandatory when calling the Exp API route,=
 this request header is <strong>mandatory</strong> when calling DSR CAP API=
. So the EXP API should populate this request header when calling DSR CAP A=
PI and pass <span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><span>&nbsp;</span>WPAC a=
s the value(<span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><span>brandSilo =3D </spa=
n>WPAC)</span></span></p></td>
</tr>
