<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">The downstream DSR CAP API will return the f=
ollowing response which will hold the Exp API payload(payments/beneficiary =
Exp API request payload) under "<span data-teams=3D"true">additionalInforma=
tion" object. The "additionalInformation" object has an attribute/property =
called "entitlementPayload" which will hold the&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: =
rgb(0,0,0);">Exp API request Payload as Json string.&nbsp; This Widget Exp =
API route will have to deserialise the Exp API Payload json object held wit=
hin data[i].additionalInformation.entitlementPayload.makerRequest.payload</=
span></span>&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);letter-spacing: 0.0px;">=
into appropriate payloads(payments payload or beneficiary payload) based on=
 the SubType.</span></p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);letter-spac=
ing: 0.0px;"><u><strong>Note:</strong></u> </span>The above deserialisation=
 approach will be adopted only for Payments and Beneficiary type/subtype, f=
or any other type/subtype(to support staff requirements), the Exp API will =
not deserialise the Exp API Payload json object held within the data[i].add=
itionalInformation.entitlementPayload.makerRequest.payload, instead it will=
 just return the Exp API json mapped against "payloadString" attribute in t=
he Exp API response</p>
<pre><br></pre>
<pre><br></pre>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">//When calling DSR CAP API to search for maker or checker workflow requ=
ests, Exp API will have to fetch the required UserID from either x-userid r=
equest header or from x-access-token request header and then pass the requi=
red userid accordingly

if(request.searchBy =3D=3D=3D "createdByUserId")
{
   var createdByUserId =3D apiHeaders['x-userId'] //or read userId from api=
Headers['x-access-token']
   // Map the above createdByUserId to DSR request.createdByUserId when cal=
ling DSR CAP API to search for maker workflow requests
}

if(request.searchBy =3D=3D=3D "approverUserId")
{
   var approverUserId=3D apiHeaders['x-userId'] //or read userId from apiHe=
aders['x-access-token']
 &nbsp; // Map the above approverUserId to DSR request.approverUserId when =
calling DSR CAP API to search for checker workflow requests=20
}


{
    "data": [
        {
            "approvalWorkflowId": "string",
            "approvalWorkflowExternalReferenceId": "string",
            "brandSilo": "WPAC",
            "brand": "WBC",
            "type": "string",
            "typeDescrption": "string",
            "subType": "string",
            "subTypeVariation": "string",
            "requestGroup": "MEDB",
            "serviceRequestId": "string",
            "serviceRequestCategory": "SimpleServiceRequest",
            "externalRequestId": "string",
            "workflowStatus": "ApprovalPending",
            "approvalWorkflowComments": "string",
            "additionalInformation": {
                "entitlementPayload": "{\r\n  \"key\" : \"ThisIsTheActualKe=
yValueButShouldBeAKeyId\",\r\n  \"hash\" : \"ff53498acdca2cc4e937b827875744=
fdc56ddf2daab0b70466582d7b4e1f7874\",\r\n  \"alg\" : \"HMAC-SHA256\",\r\n  =
\"makerRequest\" : {\r\n    \"header\" : {\r\n      \"Accept\" : [ \"applic=
ation/json\" ],\r\n      \"Connection\" : [ \"keep-alive\" ],\r\n      \"Co=
ntent-Length\" : [ \"2016\" ],\r\n      \"Content-Type\" : [ \"application/=
json\" ],\r\n      \"Host\" : [ \"localhost:3000\" ],\r\n      \"User-Agent=
\" : [ \"Apache-HttpClient/4.5.7 (Java/1.8.0_341)\" ],\r\n      \"X-Forward=
ed-For\" : [ \"172.17.0.1\" ],\r\n      \"protected-orgId\" : [ \"32896172\=
