<h3 id=3D"galaxymakercheckerwidgetexpv1-3.4DownstreamAPIInfo">3.4 Downstrea=
m API Info</h3>
<p>This route should consume the following CAP API,</p>
<ul>
<li><em style=3D"text-align: left;"><span>channel-approval-workflow-managem=
ent-v2 </span></em>API<em>, route<span>&nbsp;</span></em>POST /approvalWork=
