<h1 id=3D"galaxymakercheckerwidgetexpv1-6.Capability:Gettingtheauthorisatio=
nsummary"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);"><strong>6.&nbsp;</strong></=
span><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);"><strong>Capability:<span class=
=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"> Getting the authorisation summary&nbsp;</span>=
</strong></span></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"galaxymakercheckerwidgetexpv1-GET/activitySummary"><span>GET /act=
ivitySummary</span></h2>
<p>To retrieve a summary of authorisation activity from the Authorisation L=
og for a specific change request.</p>
<h3 id=3D"galaxymakercheckerwidgetexpv1-ResponseFieldsExplained:"><strong>R=
esponse Fields Explained:</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li><strong><code>authorised</code></strong>: Timestamp of the most recent =
approval action.</li>
<li><strong><code>authorisedBy</code></strong><span>: Approver who last aut=
horised the request.</span></li>
<li><strong><code>createdBy</code></strong>: Maker who initially raised the=
 change request.</li>
<li><strong><code>createdAt</code></strong>: Timestamp when the change requ=
est was created.</li>
<li><strong><code>updatedBy</code></strong>: Maker who last modified the ch=
ange request.</li>
<li><strong><code>updatedAt</code></strong>: Timestamp of the most recent u=
pdate to the request.</li>
<li><strong><code>updatedBy</code></strong>: Maker who last modified the ch=
ange request.</li>
<li><strong><code>ArchivedBy</code></strong>: Same as updatedBy, but it's o=
nly returned when the type/subType corresponds to a beneficiary archive. an=
d updatedBy will be null if <strong><code>ArchivedBy</code></strong> is not=
 empty.</li>
<li><strong><code>ArchivedAt</code></strong>: Same as updatedAt, but it's o=
nly returned when the type/subType corresponds to a beneficiary archive.&nb=
sp;and updatedAt will be null if&nbsp;<strong><code>ArchivedAt</code></stro=
ng>&nbsp;is not empty.</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
