n></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"galaxymakercheckerwidgetexpv1-GET/activityList"><span>GET /activi=
tyList</span></h2>
<p>Retrieves detailed logs of authorisation-related activities for a benefi=
ciary, including who performed the action, what was done, and the status of=
 the activity.</p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation"><span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluen=
ce-information-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p><span>Assume there are chance no authorisation model is enabled for the =
organisation, and the table will be displayed with no authorisation model l=
ogic.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span>In the case Authorisation model is enabled, only display fully app=
roved records to the users. (Excluding scenario whether DSR error event is =
returned)</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong>Returned Fields:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><code>date</code></strong>: Date of the activity.</li>
<li><strong><code>user</code></strong>: The user who performed the activity=
.</li>
<li><strong><code>activity</code></strong>: Type of activity =E2=80=94 one =
of:=20
<ul>
<li><code>beneficiaryCreate</code></li>
<li><code>beneficiaryUpdate</code></li>
<li><code>beneficiaryArchive</code></li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong><code>activityDetail</code></strong>: A JSON object containing:=
=20
<ul>
<li><code>accountDetail</code></li>
<li><code>accountName</code></li>
<li><code>beneficiaryNickname</code></li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong><code>activityStatus</code></strong>: Status of the activity =
=E2=80=94 one of:=20
<ul>
<li><code>Sent for authorisation</code></li>
<li><code>Authorised</code></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
